3#ifndef __NVKM_THERM_H__
4#define __NVKM_THERM_H__
5#include <core/subdev.h>
6
7#include <subdev/bios.h>
8#include <subdev/bios/therm.h>
9#include <subdev/timer.h>
10
11enum nvkm_therm_thrs_direction {
12 NVKM_THERM_THRS_FALLING = 0,
13 NVKM_THERM_THRS_RISING = 1
14};
15
16enum nvkm_therm_thrs_state {
17 NVKM_THERM_THRS_LOWER = 0,
18 NVKM_THERM_THRS_HIGHER = 1
19};
20
21enum nvkm_therm_thrs {
22 NVKM_THERM_THRS_FANBOOST = 0,
23 NVKM_THERM_THRS_DOWNCLOCK = 1,
24 NVKM_THERM_THRS_CRITICAL = 2,
25 NVKM_THERM_THRS_SHUTDOWN = 3,
26 NVKM_THERM_THRS_NR
27};
28
29enum nvkm_therm_fan_mode {
30 NVKM_THERM_CTRL_NONE = 0,
31 NVKM_THERM_CTRL_MANUAL = 1,
32 NVKM_THERM_CTRL_AUTO = 2,
33};
34
35enum nvkm_therm_attr_type {
36 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_FAN_MIN_DUTY = 0,
37 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_FAN_MAX_DUTY = 1,
38 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_FAN_MODE = 2,
39
40 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_THRS_FAN_BOOST = 10,
41 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_THRS_FAN_BOOST_HYST = 11,
42 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_THRS_DOWN_CLK = 12,
43 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_THRS_DOWN_CLK_HYST = 13,
44 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_THRS_CRITICAL = 14,
45 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_THRS_CRITICAL_HYST = 15,
46 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_THRS_SHUTDOWN = 16,
47 NVKM_THERM_ATTR_THRS_SHUTDOWN_HYST = 17,
48};
49
50struct nvkm_therm {
51 const struct nvkm_therm_func *func;
52 struct nvkm_subdev subdev;
53
54 /* automatic thermal management */
55 struct nvkm_alarm alarm;
56 spinlock_t lock;
57 struct nvbios_therm_trip_point *last_trip;
58 int mode;
59 int cstate;
60 int suspend;
61
62 /* bios */
63 struct nvbios_therm_sensor bios_sensor;
64
65 /* fan priv */
66 struct nvkm_fan *fan;
67
68 /* alarms priv */
69 struct {
70 spinlock_t alarm_program_lock;
71 struct nvkm_alarm therm_poll_alarm;
72 enum nvkm_therm_thrs_state alarm_state[NVKM_THERM_THRS_NR];
73 } sensor;
74
75 /* what should be done if the card overheats */
76 struct {
77 void (*downclock)(struct nvkm_therm *, bool active);
78 void (*pause)(struct nvkm_therm *, bool active);
79 } emergency;
80
81 /* ic */
82 struct i2c_client *ic;
83
84 int (*fan_get)(struct nvkm_therm *);
85 int (*fan_set)(struct nvkm_therm *, int);
86
87 int (*attr_get)(struct nvkm_therm *, enum nvkm_therm_attr_type);
88 int (*attr_set)(struct nvkm_therm *, enum nvkm_therm_attr_type, int);
89};
90
91int nvkm_therm_temp_get(struct nvkm_therm *);
92int nvkm_therm_fan_sense(struct nvkm_therm *);
93int nvkm_therm_cstate(struct nvkm_therm *, int, int);
94
95int nv40_therm_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_therm **);
96int nv50_therm_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_therm **);
97int g84_therm_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_therm **);
98int gt215_therm_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_therm **);
99int gf119_therm_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_therm **);
100int gm107_therm_new(struct nvkm_device *, int, struct nvkm_therm **);
101#endif
